AN ACT making appropriations to the Nevada System of Higher
Education for expenditures related to instruction that are
due to caseload adjustments at certain institutions within
the System; and providing other matters properly relating
thereto.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF NEVADA, REPRESENTED IN
